<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 03 at 5:48AM CST  by NWS Chicago</headline>
<description>...Patchy Slick Spots on Bridges and Overpasses...
Motorists are advised to be alert for slick spots on bridges and
overpasses early this morning due to patchy freezing drizzle that
will end by around 8 AM CST. Leave extra travel time. Reduce
speed and increase following distance, especially on bridges and
overpasses.</description>
